        Launch Your Career with
        <span class="text-gradient-primary">Expert Guidance</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-dark-500 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
